Hello.
New Carolina Network was originally founded by Sir Gang Shit as a result of his departure from the community of Carolina State Roleplay now known as Carolina State Network.
Sir Gang Shit grew the community to be a kind, respectful and enjoyable community which peaked at about 1,700 members.
For reasons that remain unknown Sir Gang Shit became more and more abscent from the community for longer periods of time eventually resulting in him completely cutting contact with the community and its users.
I(mxmarshall) took over running the community and successfully maintained it until its death late October 2023 when a close friend and extremely tallented user(iReflect) founded a new community of New Carolina and continued to grow it and restore it.
This repository will hopefully allow anyone who wishes to be able to continue on with Sir Gang Shits legacy and hopefully found a good community.

All discords and documents will be accessable in this repository and all my knowledge can be accessed via my Discord Direct Messages(discord: mxmarshall).

Please consider joining the following communities as they are run by some of the most loyal friends of myself and sir gang.

https://discord.gg/newcarolina

Many Thanks.
Mason Marshall | Head of security
